  "title": "The age pattern of increases in mortality affected by HIV",
  "abstract": "The motivating aim of this work is to develop new methods that can be useful in applying the HP eight-parameter model of age-specific mortality. We have done this and chosen an interesting application to demonstrate the new methods.",
